{"type":"message","id":"7e2c6e17","parentId":"f1d323d5","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:26:05.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Someone named \"名\" sent a message to 汀桑 via the delivery system. Let me check who \"名\" is - I need to look up the user to find who this is addressed to.\n\nWait, looking at the cron message: \"[cron:... 递话给名] 汀桑让我给你带句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"\n\nSo this is a delivery from 汀桑 to someone called \"名\". The cron says \"递话给名\" - this is the delivery action. But I need to figure out who \"名\" is - it's probably a user I know. Let me check my users directory to find them.\n\nActually, looking at the AGENTS.md process for 递话 (3.6):\n\n#### 用户入话通道记录\n# 从 inbound metadata 读取\n- **QQ号:** {sender_id}\n- **bot通道:** bot1 ← 新增这行\n\nSo this is a cron-triggered delivery. The message says \"汀桑让我给你带句话\" - so 汀桑 sent a message to someone called \"名\". I need to find who \"名\" is in my system and deliver this message to them.\n\nLet me check my users directory to find users whose name/nickname matches \"名\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_as8Oy6u5zwaSqz0s3s7t8227","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":189,"output":326,"cacheRead":18944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":271,"totalTokens":19459,"cost":{"input":0.00002646,"output":0.00009128000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000530432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0006481719999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277162133,"responseId":"3b791787-e6ab-4ec7-b000-e4938d3a2c44"}}
