{"type":"message","id":"bfb4da16","parentId":"dcbc784a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:26:10.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found \"名\" - their QQ ID is 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B, bot channel is bot2. The message is from 汀桑 to 名. I need to deliver this message to 名 via their bot channel (bot2).\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md 3.6, for cron-triggered delivery (\"cron 触发后的处理\"), I need to:\n- Find the user → found (名, bot2)\n- Check lastDelivered status\n\nSince this is a cron-driven delivery, I should send the message to 名 via the bot2 QQ channel. Let me use the cron tool to create an announce delivery.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - this is already a cron job firing. The cron job itself was set up to trigger this delivery. So I need to actually deliver the message to 名 via their bot channel (bot2).\n\nLet me check the encountings.md for 名 to see if there's a lastDelivered record, and then push the message.\n\nActually, for the 递话 flow described in AGENTS.md:\n```\n- lastDelivered: true → 已送达\n- lastDelivered: false → 推送失败，通知发话人\n```\n\nI need to create an announce cron to deliver this message to 名 via bot2.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_OKLLWpehgQsbwwyqrRYx4694","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B/encountings.md 2>/dev/null | tail -20"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B/encountings.md 2>/dev/null | tail -20\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":787,"output":369,"cacheRead":19712,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":282,"totalTokens":20868,"cost":{"input":0.00011018,"output":0.00010332000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0005519359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000765436}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277166924,"responseId":"e8803c74-0874-44dc-9c58-b67d5266ce14"}}
